values: Well this time next week I'll be in ocracoke with Ashleigh. A whole week to hang out with Ashleigh!!! :) Now that is what I call a vacation, a vacation that might only happen once but still this will probably be one of the best vacations I have been on.
Finally school is over and I have all summer to do nothing. :) And hopefully alot with ashleigh.

GOD!! my stupid doctor.. the subscription she subscribed me is not working! and I'am about to scream. This is like the 5th day I've had this stupid cold and I'm getting really grouchy. So who ever reads this please know not to make me mad because it'll not be pretty.

I meen lately if u notice everybody is breaking up, and I guess I'm just worried that it's working it's way down to Ashleigh and me. But really I don't want to think that because I really think Ashleigh is the best thing in my life right now, not parkside soccer coming up not anything. So Ashleigh if u read this just please know what I really do love u and that I always will.
I really have nothing to say at this point other than I love u Ashleigh and I always will no matter what :*
